# Play Store Publishing Guide

## Pre-Publication Checklist

### 1. App Bundle Configuration
- Verify versionCode increment
- Check versionName format
- Validate signing configuration
- Test bundle locally

### 2. Store Listing
- Optimize app description
- Prepare high-quality screenshots
- Create compelling feature graphic
- Write clear changelogs

### 3. Release Notes Template
